The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Gloster asked for update

Mumbai: Team India physiotherapist John Gloster has been asked to give an update on Sachin Tendulkars fitness beforer the selection of the Zimbabwe0bound squad. 

We have asked Gloster to give an update on Sachins fitness and his progress. We would be talking to Sachin too on the matter, BCCI secretary S.K. Nair said on Thursday. 

Sachin underwent surgery in London for an elbow injury at the end of May and was ruled out of cricket for 12 to 16 weeks. 

Asked about Irfan Pathans injury, Nair said his report too was awaited. 

